@node Introduction
@toc main
 
 First of all, please apologize my English ! I am French and it took a lot of time writing this english documentation.

 Icon Replacement Tool (from now IRT ;-) is a small AppWindow that lets you easily change your icons. This new version 1.6 is Shareware, so if you use it, please don't forget to @{"register" LINK Register}.

 @{"Mathieu Chčnebit" LINK Auteur}

@endnode

