@node Besoins "Requirements"
@toc main

@{u}Requirements@{uu}:
To run properly, IRT needs the following :

_ an Amiga

_ WorkBench 2.1

_ The Reqtools.library.

@endnode
@node "Life Team"
@toc main

@{u}Life Team@{uu} :

	The Life Team is a small @{b}French programming group@{ub}, which has for main goal to distribute freeware proggyes, Shareware's (and why not commercial's ;-) on Amiga. Our programms are made with the powerfull Blitz Basic 2 by Acid Software. Our second goal is to make Blitz wellknown (mainly in France), because it is probably one of the best languages.

@{u}Life Team programms :@{uu}

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} W-Anim : an IFF anim in window viewer. It has lots of functions (frame rate, palette choose ...).

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} Insulte : a program that insults you ( french only at the moment :-( ) !!!

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} LTAssign : an AppIcon that assigns files you drop on it.

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} Searcher : a powerfull file finder with a superb GUI.

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} SmallGrabber : a screen grabber with another superb GUI ;-)

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} SmallPlayer : A small module player for low-memeroy amiga

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} AppSize : An AppIcon that tels you the size of the directory you launch on it.

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} IconPlayer : An AppIcon to play .mod files.

You can find all those programms  on your favourite aminet site or at the following address :
http://www.spidernet.tm.fr/~matc999/index.html

				        @{"Author" LINK Auteur}.

@endnode
