@node Register
@toc main

 When releasing IRT as a Shareware program, I decided to do REAL Shareware. IRT is not limited in any way, but it has some requesters. If you register, you will receive a personnalised copy of IRT plus extra-bonuses from the Life Team.

 Please don't forget that when registering IRT you support the developpement of high quality software for the Amiga !

 Here are the prices to register to IRT :


		        France       USA       UK       Deutschland :  

	1   exemplar :  50 FF        $15      Ł 10         DM 20

	2      "     :  90 FF        $20      Ł 15         DM 35

	3      "     :  130 FF       $30      Ł 20         DM 50

	5     "      :  200 FF       $45      Ł 25         DM 70 


 For payment in French Francs, I can accept cash and checks. For other countries, I can only accept CASH money. My bank does not accept foreign checks.

